{"tid":159754,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯個陣比侍應問你會唔會轉位你會點","createTime":"2017-03-17T08:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T10:14:41.000Z","uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9da024b095d41b41b6488eff294a24493bc0da","tid":159754,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n去食茶記/小餐廳/譚仔 之類 有時見你人少 然後咁岩有一台人多既客入就會埋黎問你可唔可以轉位<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好撚煩 今日毒撚去食譚仔 野食都黎埋 問我可唔可以轉位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1ec8648345972a33235ba02afef18e0cfb877e","tid":159754,"uid":67047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢幫我拎埋啲野食轉嘅話我冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4ed23e6bc008029bf0a48b3a147918f84c4087","tid":159754,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主毒撚，比痰仔呀姐屌，死死地氣轉位"},{"pid":"71d58ceb33346917fcc451274af6686864b9dde8","tid":159754,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"如果識做送野 會"},{"pid":"baaa7b1e50f4795c7b87535be6d9bc0a04b7cd8b","tid":159754,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論：樓主毒撚，比痰仔呀姐屌，死死地氣轉位</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本來想叫佢將心比心<br />\n後尾諗下佢係毒撚都無可能同一班人食架啦"},{"pid":"d3e5d4531a1c2b294a1d47323df976ec1afab4e7","tid":159754,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>結論：樓主毒撚，比痰仔呀姐屌，死死地氣轉位</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本來想叫佢將心比心<br />\n後尾諗下佢係毒撚都無可能同一班人食架啦</blockquote><br />\n我同個啊姐講 唔轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f969588ec8d76a9f86dfe3dd9f8bf103e116e9","tid":159754,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":